
From hcswif directory (where hcswif.py is)

**** Replay one SHMS run ****
source replayEx/oneRun.sh

**** Replay many SHMS runs ****
source replayEx/replayTest_shms.sh

**** Replay many HMS run ****
source replayEx/replayTest_hms.sh


This will create a json file.  To send it to the farm......
where oneRun is the name of your workflow (or replayTest_shms or replayTest_hms)

******** Check JSON file *********
cd path/to/hcswif/out_dir
python -m json.tool oneRun.json

******** Create Workflow *********
swif import -file oneRun.json

******** Run Workflow *********
swif run oneRun

******** Check Status *********
swif list

******** Delete workflow *********
swif cancel -delete -workflow oneRun
